block: move GENHD_FL_BLOCK_EVENTS_ON_EXCL_WRITE to disk->event_flags

GENHD_FL_BLOCK_EVENTS_ON_EXCL_WRITE is all about the event reporting
mechanism, so move it to the event_flags field.

